ygData.messageBody:
Aye, I walk everywhere I go, sometimes it gets tedious (like when you are
bound in Freeport and die in Kaladim...ahem) but it is also a great way to
see Norrath and meet new people.

And for some reason, MOST other people rarely thank me for saving thier
lives these days..they must not know I used to be Reppik *sigh* oh well, I
guess Nylyan will have to build his own reputation for kindheartedness and
stalwartness =)
